65
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:23,160
<i>True.</i>

66
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:28,240
Well, it's better he's with his gang.

67
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,760
They'll look after him.

68
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,240
<i>Hmm.</i>

69
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,720
Sometimes, as parents,

70
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,920
we have to admit defeat.

71
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:38,760
Mmm.

72
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:43,720
<i>- All right. I'll talk to you soon.
- </i>  Right.

73
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:06,000
There are two deliveries.
This one's from the school.

74
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:09,360
More than 600 boys
felt moved to offer their condolences.

75
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,480
That's so kind.

76
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:16,720
And this one contains letters
from all around the world.

77
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:20,320
Mostly, I think, from young ladies.

78
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:25,240
If there's anything you need,
you know where I am.

79
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:01,480
<i>Dear William,
we don't know one another.</i>

80
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:04,440
<i>I'm two years above you
and in a different house,</i>

81
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:07,120
{\an8}<i>but I wanted to write
to offer my condolences.</i>

82
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:10,320
{\an8}<i>I can only imagine
what you must be going through.</i>

83
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:14,040
{\an8}<i>Please rest assured,
all of us in B block have your back.</i>

84
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,560
<i>Andrew Hartley Potts.</i>

85
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,400
<i>Dear Wills,</i>

86
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,520
<i>we're all so sorry for your loss.</i>

87
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:24,840
<i>Just know that all the boys in ALHG
are here for you</i>

88
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:26,680
<i>if you ever need anything,</i>

89
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:31,040
<i>including first dibs on the PlayStation
and unlimited cups of tea.</i>

90
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:36,000
<i>Dear William, all of us
on the water polo team are thinking of you</i>

91
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:39,000
<i>and are looking forward to having you back
when you feel ready.</i>

92
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,960
<i>Preferably sooner rather than later,</i>

93
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:44,000
<i>as Kindersley is
not a patch on you as keeper.</i>

94
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:53,320
<i>Dear William,
I feel so sad for your loss.</i>

95
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:56,480
<i>My mother has always loved
the royal family,</i>

96
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,520
<i>especially Princess Diana.</i>

97
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:02,520
<i>She said she was an angel,
and I know you're an angel too.</i>

98
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:06,760
<i>I have enclosed my picture.
My friends tell me I am very pretty...</i>

99
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:10,600
<i>Dear William,
you look so cute in a suit and tie.</i>

100
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:14,240
<i>I am sure you will look really sexy
when you have a crown on your head.</i>

101
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:17,680
<i>I bet you have a great body
as you play so many sports.</i>

102
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:20,360
<i>I've sent you my favorite teddy.</i>

103
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:23,040
<i>Like me, she's soft and cuddly.</i>

104
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:25,640
<i>Please hold her tight
when you lie in bed each night</i>

105
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:28,840
<i>and think of me.
I hope she will comfort you in your grief...</i>

106
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:33,080
<i>Dear William, you are so brave
for walking behind your mother's coffin.</i>

107
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,720
<i>I can't stop thinking about it.</i>

108
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:38,280
<i>I lost my mom last year to cancer,</i>

109
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:41,080
<i>and I think about her
every minute of the day.</i>

110
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,360
<i>I know how you feel inside.</i>

111
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,680
<i>You are not alone.</i>

112
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:48,880
<i>These people are waiting to see</i>

113
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:52,720
<i>the people's princess pass by
on her last journey.</i>

114
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:57,280
<i>And the royal family are
at the gates of Buckingham Palace,</i>

115
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:59,560
<i>waiting to do exactly the same thing.</i>

116
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,280
- Good shot, mate.
- Good shot.

117
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,640
- Great shot.
- Go on, mate!

118
