Wales... Dr. Gailey
wants to see you in his study.

119
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,240
Okay. Take that.

120
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,520
<i>For a while,
I suspect it's going to feel</i>

121
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:34,560
<i>as though the only question
anyone asks is how you're feeling.</i>

122
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:37,320
But, as your housemaster, it, uh...

123
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,800
it is actually my job.

124
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:40,760
I'm fine.

125
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:43,520
- Are you sure?
- Yes, sir.

126
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,760
I only ask
because the school has received a request

127
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:52,400
